## `.gitignore`

```gitignore
# Python
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*.pyo
*.pyd
*.so
*.egg-info/
.eggs/
.pytest_cache/
.mypy_cache/
.ipynb_checkpoints/

# Virtual environments
.venv/
venv/
env/

# Jupyter / Colab
*.ipynb_checkpoints
.env
.colab/

# OS / editor
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.vscode/
.idea/

# Logs
logs/
*.log

# Data
data/raw/
data/interim/
data/processed/

# Models / checkpoints
models/
checkpoints/
runs/

# Figures / reports (optional: keep if you want generated artifacts in repo)
# figures/
# reports/

# Streamlit
.streamlit/

# Misc
*.tmp
*.bak

.env
*.log
*.csv
*.json
*.h5
*.keras
*.pt
data/
models/
*.ipynb_checkpoints
.DS_Store